adrAdresar.desc: Update of all addresses, contacts, bank accounts and events.

adrDodavatel.desc: Update of suppliers, contacts, events and supplier's bank accounts.

adrKontakty.desc: List of all contacts that you record by companies. In the list you can search for contact by entered criterions through all companies. In update form by each company you can see contacts linked to concrete address. In contact you can enter company, position or rank, phone no., e-mail, notes and selective keys for filing and searching the contact.

adrOdberatel.desc: Actualization of customers, contacts, events and bank accounts of customers.

adrRuUdalosti.desc: List of all events from workflow

adrTypAkt.desc: Users setting of typical events or activities in your firm.

adrTypNaklAkt.desc: List of all types of costs associated with an activity or event. It includes a link to pricelist.

adrUdalosti.desc: List of all events which are conected with partner. Event can be also understood as negotiation record with partner or task which needs to be fulfilled to certain date. In address edit window you see list of events linked to selected partner. Well managed event list enables company's manger to task the emloyees and to monitor solutions status.

aktivaceProduktu.titl: Guide for activation of ABRA Flexi application

analyzaNakupuOdberatelZbozi.titl: Analysis of purchasing - Purchasing of goods based on company

analyzaNakupuWizard.desc: Analysis of purchasing can provide you with the following information: Turnover by clients / groups of clients / sold goods / groups of goods / centres etc. (assignment is in drop-down list “What do you want to analyse?”) You can also enter additional more detailed categorization (entries in the next list “What will the further categorization be?”) again based on named attributes. The result could be, for example, analysis of purchasing from individual companies with detailed categorisation of which goods the company has supplied. You will analyse everything in the particular time range.

analyzaNakupuZboziOdberatele.titl: Analysis of purchasing - Purchasing from companies according to goods

analyzaNakupuZiskOdberatele.titl: Analysis of purchasing - Purchases from companies

analyzaNakupuZiskSkupinyCen.titl: Analysis of purchasing - Purchases from price groups

analyzaNakupuZiskSkupinyFirem.titl: Analysis of purchasing - Purchases from groups of companies

analyzaNakupuZiskZbozi.titl: Analysis of purchasing - Purchasing of goods

banAkt.desc: Bank statement items update in set accounting period. Button "Services" enables print of current document, match document with invoice, debt or obligation.

banBsp.desc: List of bank accounts of the firm, including the definition of the method of electronic communication.

banDenik.desc: This will execute calculation and bank book print

banRady.desc: Document series setting for bank statements update.

banZapocty.desc: Creation of reciprocal credit is possible through wizard, where you enter a firm you do a reciprocal credit with. Then you select credit documents for accounting. To create a credit you can also do document after document, similar to the creation of bank statements items.

cenAkt.desc: Price list contains complete goods, material and service overview. Everything is classified into groups. You define goods placement in the stocks.

cenHlad.desc: Price levels create link between item group and customer group and by it clearly defined pricing.

cenOdberateleView.titl: Prices for customers/customers groups, special codes

cenSku.desc: Item and material groups enables to classify price list/catalogue to transparent groups, definition of bringing to book of these groups and also setting pricing for these groups.

cisClenDph.desc: VAT category dictates placement of document values in the VAT return. (Key F2)

cisDphPren.desc: Tax statement per §92a Law on VAT
cisDphPren.titl: List of goods with VAT transfer regime

cisZak.desc: List of orders. Each document can contains link to order. You can analyze costs of concrete order with standard summaries.

elInkaso.desc: Definition of inkaso instruction from list of issued invoices and receivables with possibility of modification. Application supports the export of instructions to most Czech banking instituitions.

elInkasoFak.titl: Selection of documents to be paid

elPrikaz.desc: Definition payment order from list of invoices in wit possibility his addition. Program support export payment order into most of banks electronical formats .

elPrikazFak.titl: Selection of documents to be paid

fapAkt.desc: Invoices in update in set accounting period. Invoicing from the stock automatically creates receipt cards. Button "Services" enables print of current invoice, gives overal information about supplier and creates cash settlement.

fapPol.desc: Overal overview of all invoice items. With help of standard filtration you create invoice items overviews or you can look for item groups according to entered criterions independently of documents. Example of use: You want to see, which companies invoiced you for concrete goods during the two last moths.

fapRady.desc: Document series setting for invoices in update.

favAkt.desc: Invoices out update in set accounting period. Invoicing from the stock automatically creates issue cards. Button "Services" enables print of current invoice, gives overal information about customer and creates cash settlement.

favPol.desc: Overall overview of all invoice items. With help of standard filtration you can create invoice items overviews or you can search item groups by entered criterions independently on documents. Usage exmaple: You want to see which companies you have invoiced for concrete goods during the last two months.

favProdPlat.desc: Payment of documents in cash register.

favProdejky.desc: Money box is designed for cash sale. It is the most simplified form of sales receipt. Once a day you upload sales to the cash desk, which is attached to the money box. Link is defined in the list of money boxes.

favRady.desc: Document series setting for invoices out update.

favTyp.desc: Invoices out types enables to set basic parameters. These are: bringing to book, payment method, document series...

intDokl.desc: Actualization and creation of internal accounting documents in set accounting period.

intRady.desc: Numerical rows setting for actualization of internal documents.

intTyp.desc: Internal document types enable to set basic parameters. Those are bringing to book, document series...

majBwithE.desc: Updates of long-term, small and nondepreciative property.

majLeasing.desc: Leasing property update, definition schedule of payments and creating accounting costs. By generation schedule of payments are automatically created debts in accounting module.

majMajetek.desc: Fixed assets, low-values fixed assets and not depreicable assets update. Depreicable assets card contain tax depreciations, account depreciation, events and registrations loans and responsible persons. You can stop depreciations anytime. You can modify depreications period during the property life.

majSazby.desc: Groups of depreciation rates contain standard values defined by current legislation. You can insert your specific depreciation rates.

majTypLeas.desc: Leasing property types enables the classfication of property into groups with advanced definition.

majTypMaj.desc: Property types enables the classfication of property into groups with advanced definition. Use of groups simplifies choice and delivers greater trnasparency.

majUmisteni.desc: Location of property pre-defined with 3 categories - building, section and room.

migraceS3.titl: Migration of agenda from Money S3

nNastav.desc: Basic company settings, company data, logo and stamp, legislative parameters and automated operations.

nezVazbyPolSklad.titl: FIFO links of issue cards disintegartion

noveSezeni.titl: Open company in a new window

obchodNapDokl.desc: You can create received supplies manually or by copying the issued demand. By copying demand to supply you save time and you must modify just prices specified by your supplier.

obchodNapRady.desc: Updates of number series for offers received.

obchodNavDokl.desc: List records all issued supplies, which were sent to your customers. It is possible to copy supply content to received order. Issued supply can be created by copying of received demand.

obchodNavRady.desc: Updates of number series for offers issued.

obchodObpDokl.desc: Received orders serve for records of requirements of your customers. Agreed sale price is mentioned in order items. By pressing one button, you can create issued invoice.

obchodObpRady.desc: Updates of number series for orders received.

obchodObvDokl.desc: Issued orders are similar (in content) with received orders. Only the ordering direction is opposite and prices are purchasing. It is possible to create issued order on the basis of received order. It means, that you will require from your suppliers only what your customers require.

obchodObvRady.desc: Updates of number series for orders issued.

obchodPppDokl.desc: Received requisiitions list records all requisitions of your current or potential customers. It is possible to copy one's requisition's content to issued supply or directly to received order.

obchodPppRady.desc: Updates of number series for requisitions received.

obchodPpvDokl.desc: Issued requisitons can be created manually or by copying the received order. Here starts the reverse process (against sale), when you need to buy goods or material from your suppliers.

obchodPpvRady.desc: Updates of number series for requisitions issued.

penizePolDokl.desc: Overview of all movements in the various lists of bank and cash modules. There are bank and cash desk items. Through standard filtering you create overviews of document items or you can search groups of movements according to set criteria, independently of documents in which the items originated.

phlAkt.desc: Updates and creation of receivables in set accounting period, which aren't placed in outgoing invoices. For example payment a rent regulation at your premises.

phlTyp.desc: #Types of other receivables enables to set basic parameters. Those are bringing to book, document series...

pokAkt.desc: Cash vouchers update in set accounting period. Button "Services" enables print of current document, match document with invoice, debt or obligation.

pokBsp.desc: Update of the cash desk list

pokDenik.desc: This will execute calculation and bank book print

pokRady.desc: Document series setting for Cash vouchers update.

polDoklNakupProdej.desc: Overviews of all movements in single lists of purchase module. Following items are concerned: received invoices, issued demands, received offers and issued orders. With help of standard filtration you can create items overviews of mentioned documents or you can search movement groups by entered criterions independently on documents in which the items were created.

polDoklPrehProdej.desc: Overviews of all movements in single lists of sale module. Following items are concerned: issued invoices, received demands, issued offers and received orders. With help of standard filtration you can create items overviews of mentioned documents or you can search movement groups by entered criterions independently on documents in which the items were created.

priznaniDanPo.titl: Balance and Profit and Loss Statements in XML

scanner.titl: Entering of amount of EAN codes

sklAkt.desc: Stock cards creation and theirs update. Stock list contains basic parameters for documents posting.

sklAktNovy.titl: Make out a receipt card/withdrawal card

sklKar.desc: Stock cards are created in price list. You will create price list item and define goods or material placement in the stocks. Here you can find overviews of stock level and movements on cards including well-arranged reports.

sklMapSklad.desc: This sets priorities of stocks use

sklPol.desc: Summary of all stock movements. With help of standard filtration you can make stock items overviews or you can seek a groups of movements by entered criterions independently of stock cards or documents.

sklPolPrehled.desc: Summary of all stock movements. With help of standard filtration you can make stock items overviews or you can seek a groups of movements by entered criterions independently of stock cards or documents.

sklRady.desc: Document series setting for receipt/issue card update.

sklVyrCisView.desc: Overview of documents of serial numbers

stavSklWizard.desc: An overview of the status of all items in the pricelist with their quantity on a particular stock to the specified date.

uSestavy.desc: Users reports seting and calculation. Function enables to you definition sever accounting report, setting accounts placement a value and activate calculation for range of months.

ucDoklUcty.desc: Update of chart of accounts and properties setting of standard balance sheet and profit and lost account.

ucetnictviPolDokl.desc: Overview of all movements in the various lists of internal receipts, other receivables and liabilities. There are items of already mentioned receipts. Through standard filtering you create overviews of receipt items of the documents or you can search groups of movements according to set criteria independently of receipts in which the items originated.

vykazPolozkyFakturOdberatelZbozi.titl: Sales analysis - Goods movements per company

vykazPolozkyFakturWizard.desc: Sale analysis will help you to provide following information: Turnover and business margin (income) by customers / groups of cust. / sold goods / groups of goods / centres etc. (entry is in roller list "What do you want to analyse"). You can also enter another more detailed classification (entry is in next list "What will be next classification") again by selected attributes. Result can be for example analysis of sale to individual companies with detailed classification of which goods which company has taken. You analyse everything in given time range.

vykazPolozkyFakturZboziOdberatele.titl: Sales analysis - Sales to companies by goods

vykazPolozkyFakturZiskSkupinyCen.titl: Analysis of sales - turnover of price groups

vykazSaldoKdatuWizard.titl: Calculation of payment balance as at

zalohaDB.desc: Backup of data on local pc. Backups can be restored also to ABRA Flexi installation.

zavAkt.desc: Updates and creation of obligations in set accounting period, which aren't placed in invoices in. For example leasing, rent etc.

zavTyp.desc: Other liability types enables to set basic parameters. Those are posting document series...
